#Text=MH : Do you think Tyra still believes her show is about finding  the next top model " even though none of the show 's winners have had that success ?

column1: #Text=WC : [ laughs ]
#Text=That is a phenomenal question .
#Text=I do n't think that the show gives its winners enough time to reign .
#Text=The show puts out two cycles a year .
#Text=While one cycle is airing , they are taping another and apparently the show is scheduled to continue until 2010 !
#Text=I think it was about finding a " Top Model " during the show 's beginnings , but I think that über-success of the show has turned it into a profit-driven production .
#Text=I just wish that the show would put more time and cultivation into their winners even after their cycle 's conclusions .
#Text=And I truly think that the show would see a return on cultivating their winners , because the show 's credibility would increase .
#Text=MH : A fan wrote in to ask , " What struggles did you face on the show as a plus sized model ?

#Text=I could n't study magazines and try to develop my poses , because a woman who weighs 110 pounds and is 5'10  looks completely different when she shapes and curves her body than a woman who is 5'10 " and weighs 175 pounds .

column1: #Text=I , therefore , had to figure things out as I went along .
#Text=The other girls had a reference/vantage point to learn from .
#Text=I 'm still figuring things out .

#Text=MH : Do you think it was unfair for Tyra to ask that [ studying magazines and developing your poses ] of you and Diana , considering that even though she 's fuller-figured now , she has a lot more experience under her belt than you two did ?
#Text=WC : Well , you know , I would say that it would have been fair if there were magazines for us to study !
#Text=But there were none .
#Text=That 's why I think that it 's so important that publications like Plus Model Magazine continue to blossom and flourish .
#Text=I 've learned more reading that magazine and getting to know the folks who write for that magazine than I ever learned about being a plus-sized model on ANTM .
#Text=P.S. I 'll be gracing the cover of that magazine in January of ' 08 .
#Text=Look out for me .
#Text=MH :
#Text=It sounds like you 're doing just fine for yourself .
#Text=Which one fan also asked , " Have you faced adversity about your weight since being on the show ?
